<td style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em;font-weight:bold;border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;border-top:1px solid #C00;padding-top:0.2em;border-bottom:1px solid #C00;"><a href="/wiki/Portal:Communism" title="Portal:Communism">Communism portal</a></td>
