<td style="text-align:right;font-size:115%;padding-top: 0.6em;">
<div class="plainlinks hlist navbar mini">
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="/wiki/Template:Platformism_sidebar" title="Template:Platformism sidebar"><abbr title="View this template">v</abbr></a></li>
