<li><i><a href="/wiki/Liberty_(1881%E2%80%931908)" title="Liberty (1881–1908)">Liberty</a></i> (US, 1881–1908)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Mother_Earth_(magazine)" title="Mother Earth (magazine)">Mother Earth</a></i> (US, 1907–1915)</li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Organized_Thoughts&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Organized Thoughts (page does not exist)">Organized Thoughts</a></i> (US, 1990s)<sup id="cite_ref-344" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-344">[344]</a></sup></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Our_Generation_(journal)" title="Our Generation (journal)">Our Generation</a></i> (originally <i>Our Generation Against Nuclear War</i>), 1961–1994; a historical and theoretical journal</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Rebelles" title="Rebelles">Rebelles</a></i> (Quebec, 1990s)<sup id="cite_ref-345" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-345">[345]</a></sup></li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Root_and_Branch_(journal)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Root and Branch (journal) (page does not exist)">Root and Branch</a></i> (Cambridge, Massachusetts, US, 1970–, featured work of <a href="/wiki/Paul_Mattick" title="Paul Mattick">Paul Mattick</a> and others)<sup id="cite_ref-346" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-346">[346]</a></sup></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Socialisme_ou_Barbarie" title="Socialisme ou Barbarie">Socialisme ou Barbarie</a></i> (France)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Solidarity_(UK)" title="Solidarity (UK)">Solidarity</a> (UK, 1960s–70s)<sup id="cite_ref-347" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-347">[347]</a></sup></i></li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Der_Sozialist&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Der Sozialist (page does not exist)">Der Sozialist</a></i>, (Germany, 1900s, co-edited by <a href="/wiki/Gustav_Landauer" title="Gustav Landauer">Gustav Landauer</a> and <a href="/wiki/Margarethe_Hardegger" class="mw-redirect" title="Margarethe Hardegger">Margarethe Hardegger</a>)<sup id="cite_ref-348" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-348">[348]</a></sup></li>
<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Tegen_de_Stroom&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Tegen de Stroom (page does not exist)">Tegen de Stroom</a></i> (1990s, Netherlands)<sup id="cite_ref-349" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-349">[349]</a></sup></li>
<li><i>Zenit</i> Sweden, 1958–1970 (Magazine by <a href="/w/index.php?title=Syndikalistiska_Gruppr%C3%B6relsen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Syndikalistiska Grupprörelsen (page does not exist)">Syndikalistiska Grupprörelsen</a>)</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
