<li id="cite_note-198"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-198">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Ernesto Screpanti, Libertarian communism: Marx Engels and the Political Economy of Freedom, Palgrave Macmillan, London, 2007.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-199"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-199">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Draper, Hal. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://jps.library.utoronto.ca/index.php/srv/article/view/5333">"The Principle of Self-Emancipation in Marx and Engels"</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20110723070247/https://jps.library.utoronto.ca/index.php/srv/article/view/5333">Archived</a> 2011-07-23 at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a>. "The Socialist Register." Vol 4.</span></li>
